      "value": "<p>At 8th level, as an immediate action upon successfully landing a melee attack on an opponent, you can choose to forgo the damage (but not any other effects of the attack) to instead affect the creature you hit as per a greater command spell, with a caster level equal to your class level. You can use this ability once per day at 8th level, and an additional time per day for every 4 levels beyond 8th.</p>\n<p>This power replaces the Staff of Order power of the Law Domain.</p>"
